<section class="about_first">
    <div class="container">
        <p>
            HSRS Global is located in Australia. We use our passion to extend knowledge to responsibly deliver information and educational rewards to the world and "to nourish and delight everyone we serve." With our focal point being quality to optimise the value for money for our clients, we are determined to strive to implement critical initiatives required to achieve our vision. In doing this, HSRS Global delivers operational excellence in all fronts the Company as well as targeting to meet or exceed our commitments to the many clients that we serve worldwide.</p>
        <p>
            With our focus on assisting our clients in achieving certifications to excel in their career, HSRS Global offers a comprehensive range of courses both online and in the classroom. We endeavour to develop and become leaders within the training industry. We work in purposeful, strategic, and resourceful ways that are imperative in learning and bettering our skills. It is our mission to work with a sense of ambition and perseverance and persist in the face of challenges, all to ensure the consistency between our actions and beliefs, and assume personal responsibility for results.</p>

    </div>
</section>


<section class="about_second">
    <div class="container">
        <p>
            HSRS Global is an accredited training organisation (ATO). We have the most highly skilled trainers in the industry and we are extremely proud of their dexterity. They are deliberately positioned to provide clients with deep industry experience and transfer knowledge through practical support post-training and pre-training. This is important in order to provide delegates with additional support and encouragement outside the class room environment. Because of this, some of our delegates have achieved the maximum available marks – Yes, elite scores of 96.2% in examinations. </p>

        <p>
            HSRS Global provides three months of purposeful coaching and mentoring in order to ensure that the course knowledge and skills has been implemented at your work place. Our classroom courses are customised to individual needs as we assess the performance of every delegate 4 times a day on average and provide tailored coaching and guidance to ensure optimal results and success.
        </p>

    </div>
</section>



<section class="about_third">
